{"tid":721564,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《PUBG》放棄控告《Fortnite》侵權","createTime":"2018-06-28T18:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T16:52:21.000Z","uid":144497,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e891b7d071a87561948447184bf2d453633c455","tid":721564,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"早前我們報導過大熱遊戲《PUBG》的開發商 Bluehole，透過韓國的子公司 PUBG 在韓國入稟，控告遊戲《Fortnite》的開發商 Epic Games 侵犯他們的版權。PUBG 指對方遊戲的殊死戰模式跟他們的相似，事實上《PUBG》和《Fortnite》都是使用 Unreal Engine 4 開發，而該引擎實際是由 Epic Games 開發和授權。<br />\n<br />\n事隔不足一個月，彭博通訊社報導指該官司已經被撤銷，但未知其箇中原因，是否 PUBG 和 Epic Games 已經達成某種和解。之前《PUBG》的開發商 Bluehole 曾經表示，《Fortnite》的玩法跟他們的越來越相似，對此表示關注。有分析認為騰訊可能扮演一定角色，因為騰訊是兩間公司的投資者之一，早前有傳騰訊有意增持 Bluehole 到 10%。<br />\n<br />\n另一放棄公司的原因，有分析認為在庭上很難證明《Fortnite》是抄襲《PUBG》的意念，訴訟勝算有限。《Fortnite》的玩家人數不斷上升，他們的盈利在今年 3 月已經超越《PUBG》，玩家人數現在已經達 1.25 億人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本好唔同<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pTzOc9LLgww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpTzOc9LLgww&d=1xL7HzWNXM%2FP0FEbg9AiAzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=51e6816f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pTzOc9LLgww</a>"},{"pid":"262e5a7b290774ad56df65300acc11840b845c79","tid":721564,"uid":58140,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"根本告唔到 傻閪嚟<br />\n抵死啦韓狗"},{"pid":"7558cf9a78f1e22ae854f0d4cd3aa7cd0c42e981","tid":721564,"uid":4557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:55:19.000Z","msg":"無知一問 點解同一個引擎出到黎差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c5ba68d4bcd9db1937fea1865d4033a008046d","tid":721564,"uid":43839,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:12:44.000Z","msg":"Fortnite 有得起野果玩法已經好唔同，可以起棟樓出黎都仲得，跟本告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5901ace6df6f8e0e6e0c116acf3aedbe2a6bf0","tid":721564,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7558cf9a78f1e22ae854f0d4cd3aa7cd0c42e981","tid":721564,"uid":4557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:55:19.000Z","msg":"無知一問 點解同一個引擎出到黎差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"引擎應該係個Frame<br />\n你可以自己改變唔同的物理參數<br />\n然後你的3D Model貼D咩質材上去又係可以完全唔同<br />\n其實除左物理同質材之外<br />\n呢兩隻GAME好似"},{"pid":"06f32b02917e534ed4e41007067390891d444ee3","tid":721564,"uid":144497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實根本係兩種風格既遊戲<br />\n唔明佢當初想告啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6647a811ba15ade8ab68cbb4eeb6a418555e5a4f","tid":721564,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"04d03fbf3ec6df76c5bf08d713bf0957972ab887","tid":721564,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"嬲撚死班pubg仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed5b47ca8c86f8404fca955f9d3bf9b1fdad3f4","tid":721564,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"訴訟勝算低藍洞無理由而加先知道，應該一個月前已經知道，佢可能係特登嚇下Eipc game同想整D官司拖延Fortnite係南韓上市"},{"pid":"7cca831ea930e4ed72d0001e9af8c27b5edb053d","tid":721564,"uid":63055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"騰訊有以下公司股權<br />\n<br />\n藍洞 10%<br />\nEpic Games 48%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結案"},{"pid":"dac3036e0560b22c39b45fe3f17b633244dd9af3","tid":721564,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"條youtu